title: Remodeled Spacious 1 Bedroom in Richmond District | Parking Available
posting_body: ['This remodeled apartment is located in a small very well maintained building (12 units in total) in the wonderful Inner Richmond neighborhood.', 'Rare nature surrounded neighborhood including Golden Gate Park, Mountain Lake Park, & the Presidio.', '505 14th Avenue is located near Clement Street on a tree-lined block.', 'The neighborhood has some of the best city living imaginable, with a friendly and diverse population, historically significant architecture, terrific public transportation, fabulous civic venues, and bustling shopping streets.', "Within walking distance is a plethora of restaurants offering an amazing array of cuisines at a price for every budget, it's possible to dine one's way around the world without leaving home.", '• 1 Bedroom w/ 1 bathroom', '• Period details throughout the unit & building', '• Unit is freshly painted', '• Beautiful Oak hardwood floors', '• Remodeled kitchen', '• Newer range & refrigerator', '• Washer/Dryer in the building', '• Water & steam heat paid for', '• Updated safety features in the building', '• Responsible on-site Resident Manager', '• Reputable Property Management', '• No pets', 'ADDITIONAL $200 FOR PARKING', 'ADDITIONAL $50 FOR STORAGE', 'Shown by appointment only.', 'Text/call for any questions Matt at', 'show contact info']
